{"tid":1657953,"cid":13,"subCid":0,"title":"仲民兩間黃店 快啲去懲罰佢","createTime":"2019-10-16T10:21:29.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-29T16:02:14.000Z","uid":187474,"like":18,"dislike":36,"uniUserReply":33,"replies":[{"pid":"f8affd309b98b6e4abf7d843db8d0c69bd350a50","tid":1657953,"uid":187474,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-16T10:21:29.000Z","msg":"仲民一早係69前出左聲，賣衫果到都有提供飯卷，但係佢兩間鋪頭都冇人去懲罰佢，雖然我都明買衫同飲酒食水煙都唔係成日可以懲罰，但係手足們都可以盡量去懲罰下，始終依家生意難做。唔通仲幫襯H&amp;M 之類嘅黑店咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nIg: <a href=\"http://galaxy.hk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fgalaxy.hk&d=TC1Ad7l9MtPLjBCdpR1LVuL6SC4MthnAeNENlMyEb%2BY%3D&h=9a82de65\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">galaxy.hk</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://instagram.com/galaxy.hk?igshid=17q04rqnv3ucd\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Finstagram.com%2Fgalaxy.hk%3Figshid%3D17q04rqnv3ucd&d=TC1Ad7l9MtPLjBCdpR1LVuL6SC4MthnAeNENlMyEb%2BY%3D&h=4a5b6280\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://instagram.com/galaxy.hk?igshid=17q04rqnv3ucd</a><br />\n<br />\nIg: galaxy.shisha<br />\n<a href=\"https://instagram.com/galaxy.shisha?igshid=835h4az7hg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Finstagram.com%2Fgalaxy.shisha%3Figshid%3D835h4az7hg&d=TC1Ad7l9MtPLjBCdpR1LVuL6SC4MthnAeNENlMyEb%2BY%3D&h=8fc09b86\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://instagram.com/galaxy.shisha?igshid=835h4az7hg</a><br />\n<br />\n利申 同仲民咩關系都冇，只係覺得依啲真黃店都冇人幫襯唔得。同埋去過佢shisha 果到同佢吹水就知佢係真黃。各位唔幫襯我覺得都可以follow 下，當係一個支持都好<br />\n<br />\n光復香港，時代革命<br />\n五大訴求，缺一不可<br />\n香港人，反抗！！"},{"pid":"f4e815d83d081ddb5a84520a31856ee9d06d16ce","tid":1657953,"uid":167548,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-16T10:22:05.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\">我要見到文宣砌成o既10.20 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\"